   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="edition" ana="#b1" xml:lang="grc" subtype="transcription" xml:id="zoor0361.transcription" corresp="#zoor0361.translation">
            <p>
               <supplied reason="lost">
                  <g type="linear-cross">+</g> Ἐνταῦθα</supplied> κῖτε
                  Νοννα<lb/>
               <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character" precision="low"/>
               <supplied reason="lost">πολι</supplied>τευομένου θυ<lb break="no"/>
               <supplied reason="lost">γάτηρ </supplied>
               <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/>, δι<unclear>άκων</unclear>,
                  <unclear>ζ</unclear>ήσασα<lb/>
               <supplied reason="lost">ἕτη</supplied>
               <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/>
               <supplied reason="lost">ἀν</supplied>απ<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">αεῖσα</supplied> μετὰ Ε<lb/>
               <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character" precision="low"/>
               <supplied reason="lost">σε</supplied>μνό <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">τητος</supplied> , μήτηρ<lb/>
               <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character" precision="low"/>
               <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">τέκν</supplied>ων, <num value="12">ιβ´</num>
               <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">Δεσίου, ἰ</supplied>νδι<lb break="no"/>
               <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">κτιῶνος <num value="10">ί</num>
               </supplied>,
                     <expan>
                  <abbr>ἤτ</abbr>
                  <ex>ους</ex>
               </expan>
               <supplied reason="lost">
                  <num value="487">υπζ´</num>
               </supplied>, ἐν τῷ
                  ἐ<unclear>ν</unclear>
               <lb break="no"/>
               <supplied reason="lost">ιαυτῷ ᾦ
                  ἀπέ</supplied>θανεν τὸ τρίτον<lb/>
               <space extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
               <supplied reason="lost">τοῦ κόσμου</supplied>.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" ana="#b1" xml:id="zoor0361.translation" corresp="#zoor0361.transcription">
            <p> Here lies Nonna, daughter<lb/>of (the) decurion? ..., (the)<lb/>deaconess, who lived
               ... [years];<lb/>she died with .... decency,<lb/>(having been) mother of
               ....<lb/>children?, on the 12th (day) of<lb/>[Daisios?, in the 10th?]
               indiction,<lb/>in (the) year [487], in the year<lb/>during which died
               one-third<lb/>[of the population].</p>
         </div>
      </body>
      <back>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>Possibly dated to 12 Daisios 487 E.P.A. = 1 June CE 592. Another inscription
               referring to a famine as the reason for high levels of mortality during this time
               (see also Fein 0001).</p>
         </div>
